{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Au Revoir - 2071</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a dystopian future with &quot;Au Revoir,&quot; a point-and-click adventure game that brings back the classic style of the 90s. In the year 2071, Au Revoir Ltd. revolutionized the world with synthetic brains that store human consciousness, allowing the rich to live forever by transferring their minds to new bodies after death. You will play as Tristan, a Sentinel for Au Revoir, tasked with retrieving these consciousnesses. During a routine mission, Tristan begins to suspect failures in his own synthetic brain. In &quot;Au Revoir,&quot; your investigative skills and choices will determine the outcome. You will face moral dilemmas and decisions that could change the fate of everyone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engaging Narrative:</strong> A rich and complex story.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/gifGameplayShort.gif?t=1738600929\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Setting:</strong> A detailed futuristic world with stunning visual effects.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/gif_hoverBack.gif?t=1738600929\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Deep Characters:</strong> Meet and interact with a variety of characters, each with their own secrets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/output-onlinegiftools.gif?t=1738600929\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Investigative Challenges:</strong> Use your skills to solve mysteries and uncover the truth. Prepare for an unforgettable journey in &quot;Au Revoir,&quot; where every decision can change the fate of everyone.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/GifPuzzle.gif?t=1738600929\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Who let the boss out?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/a8bbe32ddb9c4c219160795e081e13554af34dd2.jpg"},{"name":"There is a new manager in town","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/d1e44495d8fbcbaab415ac52808743db81675da2.jpg"},{"name":"No man standing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/23e5e9f037b77793303ac7175372d1ec86f0ff21.jpg"},{"name":"Take control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/f27c692b0a51696c443c8045eb3f30c397367dcf.jpg"},{"name":"Don't look back","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/10d1178e0fec38d9a54b8a45668e26fa44144416.jpg"},{"name":"Maniac","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/edb9754823cef15d712257f224997c9ae936802e.jpg"},{"name":"GAMER!!!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/4694e777e278a1c921a3fc187c124d69ce49f62b.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/e32d2291a9f005c6c9298d47da370161afce2fdb.jpg"},{"name":"Detective","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/4cf0cf6e0272c9618ffd018acc7a7ed33ca9144f.jpg"},{"name":"What was that?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3079600/d2b57c0a19fdaa44923937a120fbaefa17af24a8.jpg"}],"total":19},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3079600?t=1738600929","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738600929